   Create a Mad Lib Generator. 
   You may create your own story or use a famous or popular one you are familiar with.
   It should be at least 100 words long. 
   Try to use at least 1 of each of the following types of words described under Quick Review at the following link: 
   http://www.redkid.net/madlibs/
   What is Mad Libs? 
   Online Mad Libs generator should give you ideas and/or search on your own what they are and how the game works.
   http://www.redkid.net/madlibs/ 
   http://www.madglibs.com/
.
